<markdown>

In your NuGet Package Console, simply type:
> Install-Package FubuMVC.Validation

Alternatively, you can search for FubuMVC.Validation in the Package Manager.

**Is that it?**

Like other FubuMVC bottles, FubuMVC.Validation provides plenty of Out-Of-The-Box conventions that can get you started. ZERO CONFIGURATION is necessary.
